'''设置（Windows）'''，原名為“'''电脑设置'''”（'''PC Settings'''），是一款由[[微軟公司|微軟公司]]所開發[[Metro-style_apps|UWP应用程序]]，並以系統程序身分裝载于[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]、[[Windows_Server_2012|Windows Server 2012]]之后以及[[Windows_10_Mobile|Windows 10 Mobile]][[作業系統|作業系統]]之中。因大部分控制面板的操作均可直接在本程序上實現並完成，從而被認為是[[控制面板|控制台]]的替代品。

== 歷史 ==
=== Windows Server 2012/Windows 8.X ===
早在[[Windows_Server_2012|Windows Server 2012]]和[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]中，微軟公司就將其預裝在系統中並稱為“电脑设置”，其主要设计專為触摸设备而优化的简单設置介面，但可操作選項極少。<ref name="pcw-addingmanaging8">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/258875/adding_and_managing_users_in_windows_8.html|title=Adding and Managing Users in Windows 8|accessdate=20 September 2015|publisher=IDG|website=PC World|archive-date=2016-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606033531/http://www.pcworld.com/article/258875/adding_and_managing_users_in_windows_8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>自Windows 8.1作業系統後，程式得到了部分改進並添加更多的操作選項，但大部分選項仍需在原有的控制面板中完成。<ref name="ars-wblue">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/windows-blue-leaks-more-metro-more-multitasking/|title=Windows Blue leaks: More Metro, more multitasking|accessdate=January 20, 2014|date=March 25, 2013|last=Bright|first=Peter|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104134030/http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/windows-blue-leaks-more-metro-more-multitasking/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== Windows 10及未來 ===
從[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]開始，应用程序被重新設計並命名为“设置”，同時可完成大部份在控制面板中所執行的操作，並正逐步替代原有的[[控制面板|控制台]]，最終「[[設置_(Windows)|設置 (Windows)]]」[[UWP|UWP]]程式將完全取代Windows舊有的控制台，展現Windows作業系統已邁入新的里程碑。<ref name="pcpro-settingsmenu">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcpro.co.uk/software/1000331/windows-10-review-technical-preview-january-2015|title=Windows 10 review: Technical Preview (January 2015)|accessdate=7 February 2015|website=PC Pro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207210137/http://www.pcpro.co.uk/software/1000331/windows-10-review-technical-preview-january-2015|archive-date=2015-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="cnet-settingsmenu">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/windows-10-settings-menu-the-system-tab/|title=Windows 10 Settings Menu: The System tab|accessdate=7 February 2015|website=CNET|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208010206/http://www.cnet.com/how-to/windows-10-settings-menu-the-system-tab/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

因为程序本身為[[UWP|通用Windows平台]]程序，因此，也可在裝載[[Windows_10_Mobile|Windows 10 Mobile]]作業系統上的[[智能手机|智能手机]]和[[平板电脑|平板电脑]]中運行並使用。<ref name="verge-universalpreview">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7866941/windows-previews-universal-apps-for-windows-10-pcs-tablets-and-phones|title=Microsoft previews universal apps for Windows 10 PCs, tablets, and phones|accessdate=February 7, 2015|website=The Verge|archive-date=2015-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204080608/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7866941/windows-previews-universal-apps-for-windows-10-pcs-tablets-and-phones|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ars-febleak">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/02/leaks-of-windows-10-for-phones-show-us-what-to-expect/|title=Leaked images of Windows 10 for phones show us what to expect|accessdate=February 7, 2015|website=Ars Technica|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208230917/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/02/leaks-of-windows-10-for-phones-show-us-what-to-expect/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

